text: Ærest on ucingc ford of ðæs cumbes heafde on þone smalan weg þurh ðone mor to wiðigslæde þæt to brocenan beorge.
Swa forð andlang harpaðes to mægenstanes dene swa to wiðleagate<../images/tbar.gif>to nædran beorge.
<../images/tbar.gif>ðurh þone mor beriht ge mære on wiðig mor ðæt eft on ucingc ford.
Ærest of sæ up on hengestes rigc.
Swa norð andlang hricges on middeweardna sealtera cumb.
<../images/tbar.gif>be cumbe ing on holan broc<../images/tbar.gif>andlang streames ing on hlos moc.
Adune on stream on seofan æceras.
Þær of streame eft onbutan seofan æceras.
Ðæt adune on stream oð ða suran apeldran.
Ðanan eft ofer cern on gata ford.
Of earnes hlince eft ut on sæ.
Þis is seo boc þe Æþelstan cing gebocode Frithestane bisceope to Wiþiglea & to Cearn þis syndon Tantunes land.
